This website is based on the Yii Blog Demo project.

Using Yii Framework v1.1.10

The objective of this project is to enhance the initial demo version with new features.

more info soon

New Features List:

    -Wysiwyg Editor using extension xheditor-widget (http://www.yiiframework.com/extension/xheditor-widget)
    -Search Bar using modified extension esearch (http://www.yiiframework.com/extension/esearch/)

